## Part D: Phase 3.1 Walkthrough (Frontend Authentication Integration)

We implemented a premium, fully secured authentication and onboarding experience in the Next.js frontend, directly consuming the Phase 3.1 Auth module APIs.

### 1. Pages Integrated
- **[frontend/src/pages/auth/login.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/frontend/src/pages/auth/login.js):** 10-digit mobile number entry utilizing premium slate/deep-blue glassmorphic card stylings. Displays session-expiration warning banners.
- **[frontend/src/pages/auth/verify.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/frontend/src/pages/auth/verify.js):** 6-digit OTP code entry with auto-shifting focus indicators. Includes a 30s development countdown resend timer and an inline customer registration name uploader modal.
- **[frontend/src/pages/auth/register-worker.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/frontend/src/pages/auth/register-worker.js):** Multi-step worker onboarding wizard. Geolocation permissions capture coordinates dynamically; fallbacks Lucknow coordinates `[80.9462, 26.8467]` if access is denied.

### 2. Route Guards & Security
- **[frontend/src/components/withAuth.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/frontend/src/components/withAuth.js):** HOC (Higher-Order Component) checking localStorage session `token` and `role`. Displays an animated premium loading state to prevent screen flashing, and implements automatic role mismatch redirection.
- **[frontend/src/pages/_app.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/frontend/src/pages/_app.js):** Configures Axios request and response interceptors to inject authorization headers automatically and redirect 401 token expiry errors to `/auth/login?expired=true`.
- **Protected Pages:**
  - `Admin Control Panel` (`/admin`) ➔ Enforced role: `['admin']`
  - `Worker Dashboard` (`/workers/dashboard`) ➔ Enforced role: `['worker']`
  - `Worker Booking Detail` (`/workers/[id]`) ➔ Enforced role: `['customer']`
  - `Booking Tracker` (`/bookings/[id]`) ➔ Enforced role: `['customer', 'worker']`
  - `Payment Checkout` (`/payment/[bookingId]`) ➔ Enforced role: `['customer']`

### 3. Logout Integration
Wired explicit localStorage cleanup and state resets returning to the `/auth/login` redirect route upon logout across:
- **Central Admin Control Header** (`frontend/src/pages/admin/index.js`)
- **Sarthi DashboardDuty duty widgets** (`frontend/src/pages/workers/dashboard.js`)
- **Dynamic Main Header Navbar** (`frontend/src/pages/index.js`)

